# Shared by all image builds: Dockerfiles COPY the workspace and run one
# root `bun install --frozen-lockfile` (turbo prune is banned — it corrupts
# bun.lock). Keep the build context to tracked-ish sources.
.git
.turbo
node_modules
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/build
**/.cache
**/.venv
**/target
**/*.log
.claude
sandbox
packages/docs
